1
00:00:19,600 --> 00:00:22,333
I came here because I want
to apologize to you.

2
00:00:22,400 --> 00:00:26,800
Sorry if I became a villain
to all your ideas the other day.

3
00:00:26,867 --> 00:00:28,300
Apology accepted.

4
00:00:28,367 --> 00:00:31,367
Anyway, Mikoy and I talked
last night.

5
00:00:31,433 --> 00:00:33,367
And I realized that
I don't want trouble.

6
00:00:33,433 --> 00:00:36,067
I don't want negative
energy around anyone.

7
00:00:36,167 --> 00:00:38,033
You and Mikoy
talked last night?

8
00:00:38,100 --> 00:00:40,300
I wish you happiness.

9
00:00:40,367 --> 00:00:41,900
Can we still be friends?

10
00:00:41,967 --> 00:00:44,667
Of course, good friends.

11
00:00:44,733 --> 00:00:48,400
It's not yet too late for us
to be friends, right?

12
00:00:48,467 --> 00:00:52,500
And I'm sure Tiffany will
be happy if she finds out

13
00:00:52,567 --> 00:00:53,500
about this.

14
00:00:53,567 --> 00:00:55,733
Even if our family
didn't become whole

15
00:00:55,800 --> 00:00:59,000
at least we're on good terms.

16
00:00:59,067 --> 00:01:00,433
I don't want any more trouble,
Mikoy.

17
00:01:00,500 --> 00:01:03,033
It's hard to carry resentment.

18
00:01:03,100 --> 00:01:04,833
I'm sorry too for what
I've said.

19
00:01:04,900 --> 00:01:06,667
I'll say it again
I'm not blaming you.

20
00:01:06,733 --> 00:01:10,033
We have a saying that some
people met but not destined,

21
00:01:10,133 --> 00:01:12,033
- right?
- Wrong.

22
00:01:12,100 --> 00:01:17,733
Maybe you and Mikoy are destined
in the end, right?

23
00:01:17,800 --> 00:01:19,400
You know that my tongue
has a cross.

24
00:01:19,467 --> 00:01:20,433
Look,

25
00:01:21,667 --> 00:01:22,633
right?

26
00:01:22,700 --> 00:01:25,667
Everything I say will happen.

27
00:01:25,733 --> 00:01:27,167
I hope it's for everyone.

28
00:01:27,233 --> 00:01:28,633
Mikoy, please.

29
00:01:28,700 --> 00:01:29,867
Promise me.

30
00:01:29,933 --> 00:01:32,333
Say that you don't love
Celeste anymore.

31
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:36,133
And I'm the only one you love.

32
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:40,433
I promise that it's over for us
and Celeste.

33
00:01:40,500 --> 00:01:43,433
I have no feelings for her.

34
00:01:43,533 --> 00:01:46,633
I also promise that you're
the only one I love.

35
00:01:46,700 --> 00:01:47,900
It's just you.

36
00:01:47,967 --> 00:01:49,967
And I will be faithful to you.

37
00:01:50,033 --> 00:01:53,233
You have to move fast because
a few months from now

38
00:01:53,300 --> 00:01:55,533
Tonito will be married
to Celeste.

39
00:01:55,600 --> 00:01:58,400
And you know we don't want
to lose.

40
00:01:58,467 --> 00:01:59,633
Well, you never know.

41
00:01:59,700 --> 00:02:04,533
Maybe later on it's my turn
to expose something.

42
00:02:04,600 --> 00:02:05,567
I don't know, Jamaica.

43
00:02:05,633 --> 00:02:07,067
I'm just getting
this weird feeling.

44
00:02:07,133 --> 00:02:09,467
You know it's like the
grand scheme of things.

45
00:02:09,533 --> 00:02:12,400
It seems something is really
holding back our marriage.

46
00:02:12,467 --> 00:02:15,733
It seems like am I stuck
here in Sorsogon forever?

47
00:02:15,833 --> 00:02:19,833
You know it's your fault
why you're there, right?

48
00:02:19,900 --> 00:02:20,633
Hello, Love?
Hi, Love.

49
00:02:21,500 --> 00:02:22,733
How are you?

50
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:26,033
You know I was thinking we
should just get married here

51
00:02:26,100 --> 00:02:27,700
in Sorsogon.

52
00:02:27,767 --> 00:02:29,367
We can get married next week.

53
00:02:29,433 --> 00:02:31,567
Why all of a sudden
you changed your mind?

54
00:02:31,633 --> 00:02:33,800
What happened? Why are you in
a rush all of a sudden?

55
00:02:33,867 --> 00:02:36,567
I don't know. Maybe
I'm in a hurry.

56
00:02:36,633 --> 00:02:38,100
I just...

57
00:02:38,167 --> 00:02:39,433
you know, I miss you so much.

58
00:02:39,500 --> 00:02:42,967
And I just can't wait to wake up
to you every day

59
00:02:43,033 --> 00:02:45,433
and just start our lives
together.

60
00:02:45,500 --> 00:02:47,933
Okay, calm down, Love.

61
00:02:48,033 --> 00:02:49,367
Let's discuss it later.

62
00:02:49,433 --> 00:02:52,100
I just have a virtual meeting
with a group of investors

63
00:02:52,167 --> 00:02:53,300
from Thailand.

64
00:02:53,367 --> 00:02:54,433
And then I'll call you, okay?

65
00:02:54,500 --> 00:02:55,633
I love you.

66
00:02:55,700 --> 00:02:57,400
I love you too.

67
00:03:09,233 --> 00:03:10,367
Mom, look!

68
00:03:10,433 --> 00:03:11,867
It's finally here!

69
00:03:11,933 --> 00:03:14,400
Whoa!

70
00:03:14,467 --> 00:03:15,533
Mmmmwah...

71
00:03:15,600 --> 00:03:17,467
Congratulations, Tiff.

72
00:03:17,533 --> 00:03:18,900
I know you can pull it off.

73
00:03:18,967 --> 00:03:22,133
You take it from me, achiever.

74
00:03:22,233 --> 00:03:24,500
Mom, I feel it's fifty-fifty.

75
00:03:24,567 --> 00:03:27,233
Fifty percent from you
and fifty percent from Dad.

76
00:03:27,300 --> 00:03:29,133
And that makes me one hundred.

77
00:03:29,200 --> 00:03:31,667
And besides Mom, I'm not
the only one who worked

78
00:03:31,733 --> 00:03:32,900
for this.

79
00:03:32,967 --> 00:03:34,800
Someone helped me.

80
00:03:34,867 --> 00:03:37,000
The guy that I introduced
to you.

81
00:03:39,833 --> 00:03:41,867
Do you mean the guy
who helped you?

82
00:03:41,933 --> 00:03:44,467
Of course, I remember him.

83
00:03:44,533 --> 00:03:45,667
Good luck, Sweetie.

84
00:03:45,733 --> 00:03:47,367
You take care there.

85
00:03:47,433 --> 00:03:50,133
Yes, I will, Mom. You too.

86
00:03:50,200 --> 00:03:52,367
Don't forget to call me
more often.

87
00:03:52,433 --> 00:03:53,967
And call your Dad also.

88
00:03:54,067 --> 00:03:55,900
I'm sure he will be happy
with the outcome

89
00:03:55,967 --> 00:03:58,467
of your project, okay?

90
00:04:00,033 --> 00:04:02,367
I will.

91
00:04:02,433 --> 00:04:04,400
Bye, Mom. I love you.

92
00:04:09,133 --> 00:04:11,100
Oh, mmmmwah!

93
00:04:11,167 --> 00:04:13,800
Mmmmwah!

94
00:04:13,867 --> 00:04:17,467
Wow, that brown
envelope is lucky.

95
00:04:17,533 --> 00:04:19,767
You already kissed
it many times.

96
00:04:19,833 --> 00:04:21,900
Of course, This is an answered
prayer.

97
00:04:21,967 --> 00:04:24,767
I worked hard for this.

98
00:04:24,833 --> 00:04:25,967
I know.

99
00:04:26,033 --> 00:04:28,067
My neck is at stake on that.

100
00:04:31,233 --> 00:04:33,667
Are you afraid that
they will find out?

101
00:04:33,733 --> 00:04:39,900
I'm not afraid because you
can escape fear.

102
00:04:39,967 --> 00:04:42,433
But I'm guilty.

103
00:04:42,500 --> 00:04:44,733
The guilt, the shame,

104
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:48,767
the conscience you can't
escape that.

105
00:04:48,833 --> 00:04:52,667
And besides, it's embarrassing
to my townspeople.

106
00:05:07,500 --> 00:05:11,467
I don't understand why
all of a sudden Celeste

107
00:05:11,533 --> 00:05:13,067
is in a hurry for us
to get married.

108
00:05:15,200 --> 00:05:17,300
Did you tell her
about you and Aurelia

109
00:05:17,367 --> 00:05:19,133
spending the night together?

110
00:05:19,200 --> 00:05:21,167
No. I didn't bother to tell her.

111
00:05:21,233 --> 00:05:22,900
We just had a friendly dinner.

112
00:05:22,967 --> 00:05:25,767
Nothing else happened to us.

113
00:05:25,833 --> 00:05:30,133
So I have a clean conscience so
I'm not guilty of anything.

114
00:05:30,200 --> 00:05:35,067
Could it be its Celeste's
woman intuition

115
00:05:35,167 --> 00:05:36,333
that's why all of a sudden

116
00:05:36,400 --> 00:05:38,700
she's in a hurry for you
to get married?

117
00:05:38,767 --> 00:05:41,367
Do you mean she can feel
something

118
00:05:41,433 --> 00:05:42,700
between me and Aurelia?

119
00:05:43,967 --> 00:05:45,233
Maybe.

120
00:05:46,233 --> 00:05:48,133
But we didn't do anything.

121
00:05:50,033 --> 00:05:53,433
The mere fact that you didn't
tell her about it

122
00:05:53,500 --> 00:05:56,200
means you're hiding something.

123
00:05:56,267 --> 00:05:58,900
I'm sure if you mentioned
that to Celeste

124
00:05:58,967 --> 00:06:01,167
there's the possibility
that she will suspect.

125
00:06:02,300 --> 00:06:05,367
Aurelia is your ex-wife, Tonito.

126
00:06:06,400 --> 00:06:08,900
Spending the night with her
will only create doubts.

127
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:11,500
On the other hand,

128
00:06:11,567 --> 00:06:14,167
it's right that Celeste and I
are getting married.

129
00:06:14,233 --> 00:06:16,667
Because that's what we really
want to do right now.

130
00:06:18,167 --> 00:06:21,133
So when will you get married
in Sorsogon?

131
00:06:23,933 --> 00:06:25,233
Next week.

132
00:07:00,433 --> 00:07:02,033
Celeste, really?

133
00:07:02,100 --> 00:07:03,833
Next week? Here in Sorsogon?

134
00:07:03,900 --> 00:07:06,433
You and Tonito are getting
married?

135
00:07:06,500 --> 00:07:08,600
Yes, because the date
is always moved.

136
00:07:08,667 --> 00:07:11,467
So it's better to set it.

137
00:07:11,533 --> 00:07:13,900
That's good news, Celeste.

138
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:16,967
You will actually get married
here in Sorsogon.

139
00:07:17,033 --> 00:07:20,833
I'm sure your wedding
will be very beautiful.

140
00:07:20,900 --> 00:07:22,667
I should look good.

141
00:07:22,733 --> 00:07:26,300
I'll be proud that my daughter
will get married here

142
00:07:26,367 --> 00:07:27,567
in Sorsogon.

143
00:07:27,633 --> 00:07:33,633
Father, you can't tell anyone
because it's a private wedding.

144
00:07:33,700 --> 00:07:35,767
Huh? Is that so?

145
00:07:35,833 --> 00:07:38,067
I should keep my mouth shut.

146
00:07:43,167 --> 00:07:44,333
Sir, Ma'am...

147
00:07:44,400 --> 00:07:47,433
Hey, Mikoy, Hazel, come in.

148
00:07:47,500 --> 00:07:49,067
Good news.

149
00:07:49,167 --> 00:07:52,267
Celeste and Tonito
will get married here

150
00:07:52,333 --> 00:07:54,933
in Sorsogon next week.

151
00:08:12,400 --> 00:08:13,733
Really?

152
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:17,633
Oh my gosh, I'm sure it's going
to be grand and fabulous.

153
00:08:17,700 --> 00:08:19,733
Actually, it's just going
to be simple

154
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:21,200
because it's very private.

155
00:08:21,300 --> 00:08:24,367
Well if ever you need anything
I'm here, Celeste.

156
00:08:24,433 --> 00:08:27,333
I can help you with the church,
the perfect venue.

157
00:08:27,400 --> 00:08:30,067
Actually, it's beautiful in the
Cathedral of Sorsogon city.

158
00:08:30,133 --> 00:08:31,200
That's right.

159
00:08:31,267 --> 00:08:34,033
That's where Mikoy and I plan
to get married...

160
00:08:34,100 --> 00:08:35,500
right?

161
00:08:37,467 --> 00:08:39,467
- Right?
- Yes.

162
00:08:41,067 --> 00:08:42,833
Nice.

163
00:08:42,900 --> 00:08:46,933
Anyway, thank you for the offer
but I can manage.

164
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:48,833
Congratulations
to you and Tonito.

165
00:08:48,900 --> 00:08:51,167
I hope you will be happy.

166
00:08:51,233 --> 00:08:53,833
Congratulations also
to the two of you.

167
00:08:53,900 --> 00:08:55,533
I just have to take care
of something.

168
00:08:57,867 --> 00:08:59,667
Sir Patricio, by the way,

169
00:08:59,733 --> 00:09:03,200
this is the feasibility study
for our pili nut projects.

170
00:09:03,267 --> 00:09:06,700
Celeste told me that I
should give you this.

171
00:09:06,767 --> 00:09:08,033
Okay, Hazel.

172
00:09:08,100 --> 00:09:10,233
Thank you for this.
Don't worry...

173
00:09:10,300 --> 00:09:12,667
your Auntie Adora
and I will read this.

174
00:09:16,933 --> 00:09:18,500
This day is very good.

175
00:09:18,567 --> 00:09:20,933
- Very much.
- There's a lot of good news.

176
00:09:24,233 --> 00:09:25,667
Are you sure?

177
00:09:25,733 --> 00:09:28,033
I thought you're not affected.

178
00:09:28,133 --> 00:09:29,167
What's with you? Okay,

179
00:09:29,233 --> 00:09:30,733
I'll just submit
my drawings to you

180
00:09:30,800 --> 00:09:33,000
and then send that here right
away after you have it sewn.

181
00:09:33,067 --> 00:09:34,700
- Okay?
- Are you sure?

182
00:09:34,767 --> 00:09:37,633
We can't finish that
in just three days.

183
00:09:37,700 --> 00:09:41,267
Celeste, I know how intricate
your dream wedding gown is.

184
00:09:41,333 --> 00:09:44,267
Dear, you should get
extra beaders.

185
00:09:44,333 --> 00:09:45,367
Wait.

186
00:09:45,433 --> 00:09:47,467
Does the instant wedding
you want to happen really

187
00:09:47,533 --> 00:09:49,300
have something to do with the
grand scheme of things?

188
00:09:49,367 --> 00:09:51,133
Or there are other reasons?

189
00:09:51,200 --> 00:09:53,633
Maybe Mikoy's girlfriend
has something to do with it.

190
00:09:53,700 --> 00:09:56,233
Are you trying to prove
something?

191
00:09:56,300 --> 00:09:58,067
Dear, please.

192
00:09:58,133 --> 00:09:59,867
My point is I'm here
in Sorsogon.

193
00:09:59,933 --> 00:10:01,200
I'm stuck here.

194
00:10:01,300 --> 00:10:04,533
What will I do? Let's not waste
time. I should get married here.

195
00:10:04,600 --> 00:10:05,700
Oh, come on, Dear.

196
00:10:05,767 --> 00:10:07,133
I know you.

197
00:10:07,200 --> 00:10:08,233
You're not in a hurry.

198
00:10:08,300 --> 00:10:10,500
You want everything planned.

199
00:10:10,567 --> 00:10:12,167
You want everything to be sure.

200
00:10:12,233 --> 00:10:13,367
Well, I changed.

201
00:10:13,433 --> 00:10:15,033
If they want me to jump in
the river,

202
00:10:15,100 --> 00:10:16,667
I'll swim in the river.

203
00:10:16,733 --> 00:10:18,367
You're driving me crazy.

204
00:10:18,433 --> 00:10:19,967
I'm going crazy here.

205
00:10:20,033 --> 00:10:23,400
How about the church,
the venue, everything?

206
00:10:23,467 --> 00:10:26,733
That's it. Here it is.
The grand news of it all.

207
00:10:26,800 --> 00:10:27,967
Are you ready?

208
00:10:28,033 --> 00:10:31,733
The giant girlfriend of
Mikoy is willing and able

209
00:10:31,800 --> 00:10:33,033
to help me at my wedding.

210
00:10:33,100 --> 00:10:35,400
It's like she's really in a rush
for me to get married.

211
00:10:35,500 --> 00:10:36,767
I knew it.

212
00:10:36,833 --> 00:10:39,567
Mikoy's girlfriend has something
to do with the instant wedding

213
00:10:39,633 --> 00:10:42,000
that you want to happen.

214
00:10:42,067 --> 00:10:43,633
Did you ask Sir Tonito?

215
00:10:43,700 --> 00:10:45,067
Does he know about this?

216
00:10:45,133 --> 00:10:46,100
Don't you have work, dear?

217
00:10:46,167 --> 00:10:47,233
You have a lot of time.

218
00:10:47,300 --> 00:10:48,633
No, I'll call you back.

219
00:10:48,700 --> 00:10:49,900
Bye.

220
00:10:55,867 --> 00:10:57,067
Oh my God.

221
00:10:58,167 --> 00:11:00,067
My urticaria is showing.

222
00:11:00,133 --> 00:11:02,133
One, two, three, four...animal.

223
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:03,700
My God.

224
00:11:14,733 --> 00:11:16,700
Tonito is handsome.

225
00:11:17,733 --> 00:11:20,100
And he's very rich.

226
00:11:20,167 --> 00:11:22,833
He and Celeste really
good look together.

227
00:11:22,900 --> 00:11:24,933
Just because he's handsome
and rich

228
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:26,267
they look good together
right away?

229
00:11:27,833 --> 00:11:30,000
Sure, he's very well educated.

230
00:11:31,033 --> 00:11:35,133
Sophisticated and such an
opulent lifestyle.

231
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:36,833
He's every woman's dream.

232
00:11:36,900 --> 00:11:40,167
Who wouldn't like him?

233
00:11:40,233 --> 00:11:41,833
Not really.

234
00:11:41,933 --> 00:11:44,600
How about you? Is that
your dream guy?

235
00:11:44,667 --> 00:11:45,867
Of course not.

236
00:11:45,933 --> 00:11:48,033
You are my dream man.

237
00:11:48,100 --> 00:11:53,233
But for the likes of Celeste,
Tonito is the right guy for her.

238
00:11:55,333 --> 00:11:57,800
Yes, it's possible that they
look good together

239
00:11:57,867 --> 00:12:00,367
but it's also possible
they are not.

240
00:12:00,433 --> 00:12:01,467
Wait.

241
00:12:01,533 --> 00:12:05,167
Why do you seem to disagree with
everything I say?

242
00:12:05,233 --> 00:12:06,633
The least you could say
is that Celeste and Tonito

243
00:12:06,700 --> 00:12:09,067
are not a perfect match.

244
00:12:09,133 --> 00:12:11,200
Why? Who is a better match?

245
00:12:11,267 --> 00:12:12,833
You and Celeste?

246
00:12:25,600 --> 00:12:26,567
You're back.

247
00:12:27,900 --> 00:12:29,333
Where have you been?

248
00:12:29,400 --> 00:12:31,967
Obviously from another resort.

249
00:12:32,033 --> 00:12:33,933
I just had to cool down.

250
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:35,267
Hey.

251
00:12:37,767 --> 00:12:40,533
For your information,
our project was approved.

252
00:12:40,600 --> 00:12:42,300
Oh, great.

253
00:12:42,367 --> 00:12:44,100
Keep me updated on that, okay?

254
00:12:48,700 --> 00:12:50,567
Excuse me.

255
00:12:50,633 --> 00:12:52,500
Hi, sweetie.

256
00:12:52,567 --> 00:12:53,633
How are you?

257
00:12:57,200 --> 00:12:58,633
Are you home?

258
00:13:00,367 --> 00:13:01,500
Okay.

259
00:13:02,767 --> 00:13:03,933
Have you eaten?

260
00:13:12,200 --> 00:13:14,600
Come on, answer me.

261
00:13:14,667 --> 00:13:16,167
Are you and Celeste
a perfect match?

262
00:13:22,367 --> 00:13:24,167
What kind of a question is that?

263
00:13:25,267 --> 00:13:28,233
If I answer that you might
pull my hair.

264
00:13:28,300 --> 00:13:31,167
Maybe back then Celeste
and I look good together.

265
00:13:31,233 --> 00:13:33,067
But now not anymore.

266
00:13:33,133 --> 00:13:34,833
Good thing you know.

267
00:13:34,900 --> 00:13:36,733
Celeste is high maintenance.

268
00:13:37,867 --> 00:13:40,933
Just real talk, if you are not
rich as Tonito

269
00:13:41,000 --> 00:13:42,533
you will just run out of money.

270
00:13:44,567 --> 00:13:46,400
People changed.

271
00:13:46,467 --> 00:13:50,500
Maybe the simple Celeste
that you knew before

272
00:13:50,567 --> 00:13:52,033
is high maintenance now.

273
00:13:52,100 --> 00:13:55,033
Fancy and complicated.

274
00:13:55,133 --> 00:14:00,767
And maybe before she's kind
but now she's a witch.

275
00:14:03,567 --> 00:14:05,200
You know a lot has changed
with Celeste

276
00:14:05,267 --> 00:14:07,033
but she's not a witch.

277
00:14:07,100 --> 00:14:08,967
You're defending her.

278
00:14:09,033 --> 00:14:11,700
You saw what she did to me,
remember?

279
00:14:11,767 --> 00:14:13,367
She pushed me.

280
00:14:13,433 --> 00:14:15,933
If she's not a witch, I don't
know what you can her.

281
00:14:29,733 --> 00:14:32,567
I think I found the solution
to our problem.

282
00:14:39,867 --> 00:14:43,467
A partnership with Siam Global
Industry?

283
00:14:43,533 --> 00:14:44,700
Yes.

284
00:14:44,767 --> 00:14:47,367
And it's very timely, Aurelia.

285
00:14:47,433 --> 00:14:52,067
Since you and Tonito get along
very well I am sending you

286
00:14:52,133 --> 00:14:57,367
and him to Thailand to talk to
our new business partners.

287
00:14:58,867 --> 00:15:00,600
Only the two of us?

288
00:15:00,667 --> 00:15:02,333
Of course.

289
00:15:02,433 --> 00:15:06,000
And I expect good results
from the trip.

290
00:15:07,367 --> 00:15:10,133
Consider it done.

291
00:15:24,433 --> 00:15:27,333
Where is Sebastian?

292
00:15:27,400 --> 00:15:28,633
Don't look for him.

293
00:15:28,700 --> 00:15:30,000
It looks like he's courting
someone.

294
00:15:30,067 --> 00:15:33,100
He changed his clothes
several times.

295
00:15:33,167 --> 00:15:34,633
Who is it?

296
00:15:34,700 --> 00:15:36,333
I don't know.

297
00:15:36,433 --> 00:15:39,567
I'm just praying that it's a
good woman your son likes.

298
00:15:39,633 --> 00:15:42,700
So we and Celeste
can get along with her.

299
00:15:42,767 --> 00:15:45,667
So when they end up together
we can be a happy family.

300
00:15:45,733 --> 00:15:48,267
I hope so.

301
00:15:48,333 --> 00:15:52,500
Hey, Hazel, Mikoy!

302
00:15:52,567 --> 00:15:54,967
Let's eat!

303
00:15:57,100 --> 00:15:59,267
Let's eat!

304
00:15:59,333 --> 00:16:01,133
Everything is okay, right?

305
00:16:01,200 --> 00:16:02,533
Come on.

306
00:16:02,600 --> 00:16:05,100
Mikoy, Hazel, sit here.

307
00:16:05,167 --> 00:16:06,967
We're going to eat.

308
00:16:08,633 --> 00:16:09,567
Where is Celeste?

309
00:16:09,633 --> 00:16:12,800
I already called her.
She will follow.

310
00:16:12,867 --> 00:16:13,767
This is delicious.

311
00:16:15,000 --> 00:16:16,467
You should eat well.

312
00:16:16,533 --> 00:16:18,767
You go ahead. We'll follow.

313
00:16:18,833 --> 00:16:20,667
I'm really hungry.

314
00:16:22,333 --> 00:16:23,867
Get some more.

315
00:16:23,933 --> 00:16:27,133
You should eat a lot
so you will be full.

316
00:16:29,400 --> 00:16:31,400
So, I'm a witch.

317
00:16:33,300 --> 00:16:34,900
Oh my God!

318
00:16:34,967 --> 00:16:36,267
- Are you okay?
- Are you okay?

319
00:16:37,667 --> 00:16:39,067
So I'm a witch.

320
00:16:41,233 --> 00:16:42,833
Oh my God!

321
00:16:42,933 --> 00:16:44,800
- Are you okay?
- Are you okay?

322
00:16:44,867 --> 00:16:46,400
Are you okay?

323
00:16:46,467 --> 00:16:47,400
Why? What happened?

324
00:16:47,467 --> 00:16:48,500
What was that?

325
00:16:48,567 --> 00:16:50,433
Come here.

326
00:16:50,500 --> 00:16:52,267
Are you okay?

327
00:16:52,333 --> 00:16:54,533
What happened?

328
00:16:54,600 --> 00:16:56,533
I'm okay. Thank you.

329
00:16:56,600 --> 00:17:00,467
Maybe she kicked the chair
when she was about to sit down.

330
00:17:00,533 --> 00:17:01,533
Does it hurt?

331
00:17:01,600 --> 00:17:03,600
She said it's nothing.

332
00:17:03,667 --> 00:17:04,833
Are you okay?

333
00:17:04,900 --> 00:17:06,000
I'm okay.

334
00:17:07,000 --> 00:17:09,167
Hazel, you should avoid
accidents.

335
00:17:09,233 --> 00:17:11,333
Be careful next time.

336
00:17:11,400 --> 00:17:13,700
I was startled.

337
00:17:13,767 --> 00:17:15,567
You're our visitor.

338
00:17:15,667 --> 00:17:18,200
I'll keep that in mind.

339
00:17:18,267 --> 00:17:19,800
You should eat.

340
00:17:19,867 --> 00:17:21,267
The food is delicious.

341
00:17:21,333 --> 00:17:24,667
Oh my God you have prosciutto.

342
00:17:24,733 --> 00:17:26,633
I'm so hungry.

343
00:18:00,633 --> 00:18:01,833
What?

344
00:18:01,900 --> 00:18:04,100
Celeste did that to you?

345
00:18:04,167 --> 00:18:05,933
She pulled your chair?

346
00:18:09,833 --> 00:18:11,067
I'm sorry.

347
00:18:11,133 --> 00:18:13,600
I just laughed.

348
00:18:13,667 --> 00:18:16,633
How can you say that she did it?

349
00:18:16,700 --> 00:18:17,733
Grandmother Ikay,

350
00:18:17,800 --> 00:18:19,567
she was the last to arrive.

351
00:18:19,633 --> 00:18:22,633
And it just so happen she was at
my back when it happened.

352
00:18:22,733 --> 00:18:24,433
Who else should I accuse?

353
00:18:24,500 --> 00:18:27,467
A ghost?

354
00:18:27,533 --> 00:18:30,967
That's not how I knew Celeste.

355
00:18:31,033 --> 00:18:34,400
That's how witch she is,
Grandmother Ikay.

356
00:18:34,467 --> 00:18:38,033
I'm absolutely right that she
should not be trusted.

357
00:18:38,100 --> 00:18:40,133
She attacks behind your back.

358
00:18:43,200 --> 00:18:46,533
If you two won't stop,
nothing will happen to you.

359
00:18:46,600 --> 00:18:48,500
You are like children.

360
00:18:48,567 --> 00:18:53,300
You know I really don't believe
her apology yesterday.

361
00:18:53,367 --> 00:18:57,367
As long as she's here in
Sorsogon I can't be at peace.

362
00:19:05,967 --> 00:19:07,200
Coffee?

363
00:19:10,300 --> 00:19:12,300
Why did you do that?

364
00:19:12,367 --> 00:19:13,600
I don't know. I was also
surprised

365
00:19:13,667 --> 00:19:15,100
at myself when I did that.

366
00:19:15,167 --> 00:19:18,467
You know I also feel guilty
because I'm not a bad person.

367
00:19:18,533 --> 00:19:21,533
But I was annoyed because
she called me a witch.

368
00:19:21,600 --> 00:19:23,033
Is that really what
pissed you off

369
00:19:23,100 --> 00:19:24,667
or it is because she said that
you and Mikoy

370
00:19:24,733 --> 00:19:25,700
don't look good together?

371
00:19:25,767 --> 00:19:27,600
Dear, I was the first.

372
00:19:27,667 --> 00:19:29,067
If I went with Mikoy back
to Sorsogon,

373
00:19:29,167 --> 00:19:31,233
then they won't be together now.

374
00:19:31,300 --> 00:19:34,600
Why are you pissed off
with that Hazel?

375
00:19:34,667 --> 00:19:36,900
Why are you so affected by her?

376
00:19:36,967 --> 00:19:37,900
She is annoying.

377
00:19:37,967 --> 00:19:39,800
The tall girl is so daring.

378
00:19:39,867 --> 00:19:41,667
She is very hard...

379
00:19:41,733 --> 00:19:44,533
the nerve to tell me that Mikoy
and I don't look good together.

380
00:19:44,600 --> 00:19:46,000
Why? Do they look good together?

381
00:19:46,067 --> 00:19:47,800
She's right, isn't she?

382
00:19:47,867 --> 00:19:50,767
You and Mikoy are no match,
Celeste.

383
00:19:50,833 --> 00:19:52,400
Look at you now...

384
00:19:52,467 --> 00:19:54,867
Rubbing elbows with the rich
and famous.

385
00:19:54,933 --> 00:19:58,000
Living the glitz and glamour
of high society.

386
00:19:58,067 --> 00:20:00,333
You and Tonito are a perfect
match.

387
00:20:00,400 --> 00:20:03,833
Mikoy will just look like
your driver.

388
00:20:03,933 --> 00:20:05,033
Dear, that's harsh.

389
00:20:05,100 --> 00:20:06,300
That's bad.

390
00:20:06,367 --> 00:20:07,767
Don't be like that.

391
00:20:07,833 --> 00:20:09,400
I'm pissed off.

392
00:20:09,467 --> 00:20:10,433
She's so hard.

393
00:20:10,500 --> 00:20:11,867
Let's not talk about her.

394
00:20:11,933 --> 00:20:13,333
Annoying.

395
00:20:13,400 --> 00:20:15,933
I don't want people
talking about me.

396
00:20:16,000 --> 00:20:17,333
So this is it.

397
00:20:17,400 --> 00:20:19,733
Aren't you the one getting
married next week?

398
00:20:19,800 --> 00:20:21,833
Where is the design
of your gown?

399
00:20:21,900 --> 00:20:22,900
My gosh. Here it is.

400
00:20:22,967 --> 00:20:24,833
It's your fault. You keep on
tik-tak-tik-tak.

401
00:20:24,900 --> 00:20:26,567
What's the vocabulary?

402
00:20:26,633 --> 00:20:28,167
Tik-tak-tik-tak talk.

403
00:20:28,233 --> 00:20:29,733
Oh my, it's the exposure, Dear.

404
00:20:29,800 --> 00:20:31,500
Stop Okay, bye.

405
00:20:39,433 --> 00:20:40,733
Celeste is something else...

406
00:20:59,233 --> 00:21:01,867
you're annoying. Okay.
Start again... scratch.

407
00:21:13,133 --> 00:21:14,333
Are you kidding me?

408
00:21:14,400 --> 00:21:17,367
I thought it's the two of us
who are going to Thailand.

409
00:21:17,433 --> 00:21:20,300
What's wrong if it's you
and Aurelia

410
00:21:20,367 --> 00:21:22,367
who will represent the company?

411
00:21:22,433 --> 00:21:25,533
After all, she is our
shareholder.

412
00:21:26,267 --> 00:21:30,167
You know that's not
her forte, Vivian.

413
00:21:30,233 --> 00:21:32,200
She's into fashion design.

414
00:21:32,267 --> 00:21:34,767
And then you will
make her do this?

415
00:21:34,833 --> 00:21:39,467
Tonito, don't underestimate
Aurelia's ability.

416
00:21:39,533 --> 00:21:42,567
Don't forget she
is a businesswoman.

417
00:21:42,667 --> 00:21:43,833
Yes, I know.

418
00:21:43,900 --> 00:21:45,267
But it would be better for
the company

419
00:21:45,333 --> 00:21:47,900
if both of us were there
to represent it.

420
00:21:47,967 --> 00:21:50,433
What really is the problem,
Tonito?

421
00:21:50,500 --> 00:21:52,233
Is this about Celeste?

422
00:21:54,600 --> 00:22:01,167
Tonito, your personal agenda has
nothing to do with our business.

423
00:22:01,233 --> 00:22:04,400
If what you need to do for the
company will be an issue

424
00:22:04,467 --> 00:22:05,967
with Celeste,

425
00:22:06,033 --> 00:22:09,300
well you better talk to her now

426
00:22:09,367 --> 00:22:13,333
because this is not the only
engagement you and Aurelia

427
00:22:13,400 --> 00:22:14,733
will do for the company.

428
00:22:16,500 --> 00:22:22,167
If Celeste will stop you,
we will have a problem.

429
00:22:22,233 --> 00:22:25,067
We cannot lose this opportunity,
Tonito.

430
00:22:45,667 --> 00:22:47,933
Hello, Love.

431
00:22:48,000 --> 00:22:51,100
Hi love. Are you still busy?

432
00:22:51,200 --> 00:22:53,533
I was about to call you.

433
00:22:53,600 --> 00:22:55,500
You sound exhausted.

434
00:22:55,567 --> 00:22:58,433
Do you want us to talk some
other day?

435
00:22:58,500 --> 00:23:00,700
Yeah, better.

436
00:23:00,767 --> 00:23:06,267
I don't think my brain can
absorb all information.

437
00:23:06,333 --> 00:23:08,767
Okay.

438
00:23:08,833 --> 00:23:10,400
You should rest.

439
00:23:10,467 --> 00:23:12,600
I love you.

440
00:23:12,667 --> 00:23:14,233
I love you more.

441
00:23:44,300 --> 00:23:46,300
What's wrong with me?

442
00:23:46,367 --> 00:23:48,633
Why can't I concentrate?

443
00:24:03,367 --> 00:24:05,000
Hello?

444
00:24:05,067 --> 00:24:09,067
Hello, Celeste? Are you sleeping
already?

445
00:24:09,133 --> 00:24:14,367
I just want to remind you of
your community service tomorrow.

446
00:24:14,433 --> 00:24:16,267
Where are we going tomorrow?

447
00:24:16,333 --> 00:24:18,867
In Irosin. We're going to do
tree planting.

448
00:24:18,933 --> 00:24:21,133
Do you remember that place?

449
00:24:21,200 --> 00:24:23,533
We often go there when we were
teenagers.

450
00:24:23,600 --> 00:24:24,900
That's where I shouted
that I love you so much

451
00:24:24,967 --> 00:24:26,667
for the first time.

452
00:24:28,500 --> 00:24:30,867
Alright.

453
00:24:30,967 --> 00:24:32,533
Okay. Goodnight.

454
00:25:33,000 --> 00:25:35,833
They were supposed to get
married in four months.

455
00:25:35,933 --> 00:25:36,967
Why did it change?

456
00:25:37,033 --> 00:25:39,200
Tonito felt our plans.

457
00:25:39,267 --> 00:25:41,067
Sebastian often visits us.

458
00:25:41,133 --> 00:25:42,467
He's with his girlfriend.

459
00:25:42,533 --> 00:25:43,567
- Girlfriend?
- Girlfriend?

460
00:25:43,633 --> 00:25:45,233
She is beautiful.

461
00:25:45,300 --> 00:25:48,867
Surprise!

462
00:25:48,933 --> 00:25:51,033
Happy anniversary!

463
00:25:51,100 --> 00:25:52,067
Something came up.

464
00:25:52,133 --> 00:25:53,133
Why? What happened?

465
00:25:53,200 --> 00:25:54,167
I'm going to Thailand.

466
00:25:54,233 --> 00:25:55,533
Are you traveling alone?

467
00:25:55,600 --> 00:25:56,833
Aurelia is going with me.

468
00:25:56,900 --> 00:25:59,800
I will do everything
that I can to make him

469
00:25:59,867 --> 00:26:02,033
fall in love with me again.

470
00:26:02,100 --> 00:26:03,867
Remember whoever you love,

471
00:26:03,933 --> 00:26:05,900
your father and I will
love her too.

472
00:26:05,967 --> 00:26:06,900
Of course.

473
00:26:06,967 --> 00:26:08,433
Mikoy is really doing it
on purpose.

474
00:26:08,500 --> 00:26:12,400
He takes me to places
full of our memories.

475
00:26:12,500 --> 00:26:13,867
I don't want to fool you.

476
00:26:13,933 --> 00:26:15,300
I'm sorry.

477
00:26:15,367 --> 00:26:17,167
I pity my parents.

478
00:26:17,233 --> 00:26:19,300
I can't give you a chance,
Tiffany.

479
00:26:19,367 --> 00:26:21,433
Hello, Mikoy? Mikoy,
there's a problem.

480
00:26:21,500 --> 00:26:22,400
What happened?

481
00:26:22,467 --> 00:26:25,633
Celeste is missing.
We can't find her.
